  "subject": "Change psycopg install from binary to source",
  "commit_message": "Change psycopg install from binary to source\n\nAs recommended by the docs:\n\nhttps://www.psycopg.org/docs/install.html#install-from-source\n\n\"The psycopg2-binary package is meant for beginners to start playing\nwith Python and PostgreSQL without the need to meet the build\nrequirements.\"\n\nIssue-ID: DCAEGEN2-2720\nSigned-off-by: Alexander Mazuruk <a.mazuruk@samsung.com>\nChange-Id: I172225f61afa55b11ef72557c6f86dad8d83a30b\n",
